<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n42023e"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n42" href="#n42023e">N42 (VI.B.31)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n42all.htm#n42023e"> 23(e)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> I clean thee / unclean &mdash;</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">So Christ had given to His apostles, and His whole Church equally, infallible rules and marks to determine whether or not the spiritual leprosy was gone, that they might clean the leper and tell him, I clean thee  <font color="green">[vertical bar]</font>I forgive thy sins, or <font color="green">[vertical bar]</font> or I unclean thee <font color="green">[vertical bar]</font> I retain thy sins <small> Chiniquy, <a name="CPWC" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#CPWC"><cite title="source">The Priest The Woman and The Confessional</cite></a> (n.d.) 113</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
